To the person referring to the fact that the peacekeepers could not fire unless fired upon, you are right. I belive there was an incident where an entire refugee camp got massacred because the peacekeepers could not do jack $#!+ due to the ROE. I think it was the Belgian peacekeepers that all burned their blue berets in protest.<br>
<br>
Sorry I have just seen to much suffering in my life to put up with someone bent on causing more without thinking. <br>
<br>
As to all the French basing, it's just funny how people think its funny to show just how ignorant they are <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . Ignorance is bliss!<br>
<br>
Taranna you really are Al's friend, your just more coherent and easier to follow.<br>
<br>
Think thats all I have to say. prolly be more when I re-read this thread a second time. <br>
